  Constructions](papers/gobeski-morzycki18.pdf)*’. In [_Proceedings of
  Semantics and Linguistic Theory (SALT) 27_][SALT27].
  Dan Burgdorf, Jacob Collar, Sireemas Maspong, and Brynhildur
