  (abs): Among the more intuitively appealing and elegant ideas in the
  analysis of adjectives is that they denote measure functions (Kennedy
  1999). But as Bale 2007 pointed out, conjoined adjectives are problematic
  for this view. He, Schwarz 2010, Schwarzschild 2013, and have wrestled
